 a much\nlarger number. The relations of these polynomials to the polynomial spin\nentanglement invariants of three and four non-relativistic spin-$\\frac{1}{2}$\nparticles are described.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 16 May 2021 19:40:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 10 Jun 2021 12:30:53 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 25 Feb 2022 03:19:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-28"}
